721944f-b.text:
(1)
Norfolk Street, (rear view) west side, south from but not including Delancey, to but not including Broome Streets, as seen from clearance on Essex Street. The view shows a 3-story frame building at the rear of No. 81 Norfolk Street.

1932.

J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 394.

(2)
The same, showing only the rears of Nos 81 and 83.

May 9, 1930.

P. L. Sperr.
